  T -->|Who calls it| Callers["codegraph_callers"]
  T -->|What it calls| Callees["codegraph_callees"]
  T -->|Change impact| Impact["codegraph_impact"]
  T -->|Read indexed file or symbol| Node["codegraph_node"]
  T -->|Index health| Status["codegraph_status"]
  Explore --> H["ToolHandler validates input and output budget"]
  Search --> H
  Callers --> H
  Callees --> H
  Impact --> H
  Node --> H
  Status --> H
  H --> CG["CodeGraph instance"]
